            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 3-4 min turn the <strong>hake fillet[s]</strong> and add the <strong>sticky sauce </strong>to the pan</p><p>Cook for a further 3-4 min or until the hake is cooked through and the sauce has thickened to a sticky consistency – these are your <strong>sticky Chinese-style hake fillet[s]</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 6,
